// Wizard
// Multi-step wizard with a progress indicator, back/next navigation, and optional skip.
// Each step renders its own content; navigation is gated by step validation.

FUNCTION handleNext()
  IF current step has a validation function, runs it.
  IF validation passes (or no validation), advances to the next step.
  IF on the last step, calls onComplete.

---

FUNCTION handleBack()
  Decrements the current step index.

---

FUNCTION handleSkip()
  Advances to the next step without validation.
  Only available for steps marked as skippable.

---

FUNCTION Wizard(props) -> ReactNode                                       EXPORT
  Renders the current step's content with its title and description.
  Shows a step progress indicator (e.g., "Step 2 of 4").
  Renders Back, Skip (if applicable), and Next/Finish buttons.
  Disables Back on the first step.
